Requirement

I’m in charge of the interface design and interworking for various large projects, which covers participating in the preliminary requirements analysis, confirming project content, launching task assignment and hosting the feedback&summary meeting.

User research

Through in-depth research, we develop a holistic understanding of an audience — identifying their behaviors and genuine needs, thus uncovering new design opportunities. These insights shape our entire process and help us make informed decisions along the way.

User experience design

User experience analysis and research: Familiar with total procedure of user experience and kinds of research. Better capability of translating into experience results for documents.

Interaction design

In order to complete an efficient and unified design in the team, I, the team leader, will work together with my coworkers to make the UI interaction rules and keep studying the essence of interaction design of both ios design and material design.

Keep learning

What’s more, with the goal of building a stronger and more cooperative design team, it is vital to learn the up-to-date design software and organize some trainings on a regular basis.

Design trend

Design trends and competitors (products) research. Professional perspective of trends analysis, excellent data modeling with analysis ability both competing product analysis ability.

Multi-language

I'm responsible for the communication and negotiation of large-scale projects such as CIIF. In addition, equipped with multi-language and distinguished oratorical ability

Teamwork

We are aimed at establishing a design mechanism combined with efficiency feedback and revision, thus accomplishing interface design and interworking and ultimately passing the internal and external audit.
